msgid "RACE_HUMAN_NAME"
msgstr "Human"

msgid "RACE_HUMAN_DESC"
msgstr "You are an ordinary human."

msgid "RACE_FOX_NAME"
msgstr "Fox Yao"

msgid "RACE_FOX_DESC"
msgstr "Fox yao are naturally clever, skilled at reading expressions and moods, often striking in appearance, and commonly seen as having an innate affinity for opportunity and social ties."

msgid "RACE_WOLF_NAME"
msgstr "Wolf Yao"

msgid "RACE_WOLF_DESC"
msgstr "Wolf yao have strong bloodlines, value survival, hunting, and battle, possess keen instincts and swift movement, and often temper their cultivation through combat."

msgid "RACE_BIRD_NAME"
msgstr "Bird Yao"

msgid "RACE_BIRD_DESC"
msgstr "Bird yao have broad perception and nimble movement, are born to yearn for distant places, and excel at scouting, escape, and exploring the unknown."

msgid "RACE_SNAKE_NAME"
msgstr "Snake Yao"

msgid "RACE_SNAKE_DESC"
msgstr "Snake yao have subtle auras and patient ways, excel at hiding and ambush, are often feared by human cultivators, and adapt well to dark and dangerous places."

msgid "RACE_TURTLE_NAME"
msgstr "Turtle Yao"

msgid "RACE_TURTLE_DESC"
msgstr "Turtle yao are long-lived and steady of body, slow and cautious in conduct, and most skilled at defense, recuperation, and long secluded cultivation."
